notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: J.C., B.Z. contributed to the conception and design of the study and data analysis; K.L., W.D. and J.C. collected the plant material and performed distillation and GC-MS analysis; K.L., S.C. and W.H. carried out bioactivity test; K.L. and J.C. wrote the manuscript. All authors reviewed and approved the manuscript.
